methods.label: RawTime
methods.comment:
Date and Time the object was instantiated, as a Variant of DataType 7 (Date/Time).
A date/time value is an eight-byte floating-point value. 
The integer part represents a serial day counted from the date January 1, 100 AD. 
The fractional part represents the time as a fraction of a day, measured from midnight on the preceding day.
date / time of instantiation
methods.signature: Public Property Get RawTime As Double
methods.commentblock: <div class="description">	<ul class="blockList">		<li class="blockList">			<div class="comments"><!-- comment --><pre>Date and Time the object was instantiated, as a Variant of DataType 7 (Date/Time).<br />A date/time value is an eight-byte floating-point value. <br />The integer part represents a serial day counted from the date January 1, 100 AD. <br />The fractional part represents the time as a fraction of a day, measured from midnight on the preceding day.<br />date / time of instantiation</pre></div>			<hr />		</li>	</ul></div>
